class.abstract: The collection of all the Sampled objects currently contained in the current document.

class.abstract: The collection of all shot objects contained in the current sampled.

method.abstract: Adds a shot to a specific location to the shots collection.

method.name: Item
method.abstract: Returns a shot using its index from the colection.

method.name: Remove
method.abstract: Removes a shot from the collection.
